31\. "And the Elohim said, let there be light, and there was light."
(The sense may be sought from that Psalm xxxiii. 9) where it a written,
"Since He Himself spake, and it was done." (First, therefore, is
commemorated) the Path HVA, *Hoa*, (that is, the mother of
